{"tid":2333000,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲一眼從 TWICE 認出周子瑜！整片「平坦蠻腰」外露超吸睛","createTime":"2020-12-20T05:25:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T07:28:02.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e1e3d3ddefe70332e58ba8c0e67b5f4b1b3b95aa","tid":2333000,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:25:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/12/20/201220-15231-1-S56dJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F201220-15231-1-S56dJ.jpg&h=d8ca8421&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 官方社群昨天（19日）曝光一段成員身穿白色造型熱舞的影片，其中周子瑜白色短 T 搭配白色長褲，長腿及蠻腰成為特色，隱匿在全身都是白色的團員中，還是讓粉絲一眼認出來。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE 經紀公司官方社群分享了一段成員們在練舞教室排練《CRY FOR ME》的片段，全員穿上白色系的休閒造型，短版緊身 T 恤搭配白色的長褲或短褲，整齊劃一的舞步讓粉絲看得目瞪口呆。而其中來自台灣的周子瑜，是成員中唯一穿短袖的，加上一頭金色長髮，大方秀出纖細手臂、白皙蠻腰及逆天長腿，辨識度超高。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/12/20/201220-15231-2-2V6Xu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F201220-15231-2-2V6Xu.jpg&h=4a8203b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/12/20/201220-15231-3-HaWdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F201220-15231-3-HaWdv.jpg&h=600e8ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE 曝光了《CRY FOR ME》練舞片段。<br />\n<br />\n周子瑜短袖緊身 T 恤的短版剪裁讓她露出了一大截平坦蠻腰，下半身則是搭配白色稍微寬鬆的長褲以及白色球鞋，其中獨舞片段扭腰擺臀的動作更是性感逼人，TWICE 官方 IG 也釋出了練舞的團體照，子瑜修長身型即便隱匿團員中，依然超級亮眼。<br />\n<br />\n許多粉絲看到練舞片段及照片後，紛紛留言對周子瑜表示讚美「即使大家都穿一樣我眼裡只有子瑜」「我家子瑜腿也太長了吧」、「光看小蠻腰就知道那是周子瑜」、「便服造型也這麼辣」、「子瑜不要冷到了喔」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/12/20/201220-15231-4-RJ4ev.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F201220-15231-4-RJ4ev.jpg&h=6bfa825a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/12/20/201220-15231-5-8Wqhv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F12%2F20%2F201220-15231-5-8Wqhv.jpg&h=d82e453a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ad4330d5e8db82563037647e8282c6c78f10420","tid":2333000,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"我夠可以一眼認出牙南啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35063230e79463f6627d2c20445b07a3fe82e330","tid":2333000,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"娜璉一個著短褲勁淫勁機心"},{"pid":"046762843e4c6799a9016707e1b502b99e0b2589","tid":2333000,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35063230e79463f6627d2c20445b07a3fe82e330","tid":2333000,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"娜璉一個著短褲勁淫勁機心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"你好lum佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ed0bd107fd2d2017190e8b7df1ce67b9f46a15","tid":2333000,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad4330d5e8db82563037647e8282c6c78f10420","tid":2333000,"uid":229026,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"我夠可以一眼認出牙南啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:37:56.000Z","msg":"會唔會太勁(癲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8